            {
                "category": "summary",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA Transformers4Rec.&nbsp;<br>To protect your system, update NVIDIA Transformers4Rec to commit <a href=\"https://github.com/NVIDIA-Merlin/Transformers4Rec/commit/8bf122f5dcb39feecfc6dabde734d79c2d1c4380\">8bf122f</a> or later.&nbsp;",
                "title": "Summary"
            },
            {
                "category": "details",
                "text": "To protect your system, update Transformers4Rec to commit <a href=\"https://github.com/NVIDIA-Merlin/Transformers4Rec/commit/8bf122f5dcb39feecfc6dabde734d79c2d1c4380\">8bf122f</a> or later.&nbsp;",
                "title": "Security Update Notes"
            },
            {
                "category": "details",
                "text": "Refer to Security Updates for the updated versions to install.",
