            "notes": [
                {
                    "category": "summary",
                    "text": "NVIDIA Tranformers4Rec contains a vulnerability where an attacker could cause improper deserialization of untrusted data. A successful exploit of this vulnerability might lead to code execution, data tampering, and information disclosure.",
